content.rendered:
Reading Time: 3 minutes

A new life is blooming for Amber Rose.

Much to the very pleasant surprise of her social media followers and fans.

The 35-year old model shocked supporters on Wednesday evening by sharing a rather revealing photo of herself at the doctor’s office.

In the image, which we’ve posted below, Rose’s top is hiked up, a medical instrument is placed over her belly and there’s a rather precious picture on the monitor next to her.

Indeed: It’s an ultrasound appointment.

Because Rose is pregnant!

“@ae4president and I are SUPER excited to announce that we have a Sweet little Baby Boy on the way!” Amber wrote as a caption to this unexpected snapshot, adding of her first child:

“P.S Sebastian is soooooo Happy to be a big brother!”

Rose and Alexander Edwards have been dating since September of 2018, making their public debut a few weeks later at Rose’s fourth annual SlutWalk.

The latter published this same photograph of Rose on his Instagram account and included the following words alongside it:

Even when it’s dark.. my SON will shine.

Thank u baby 4 my greatest gift. shit wild! I love you. I can’t wait to thug it out w my baby boy. & baby boy, I promise I won’t get mad if ur first words r “where the bitches @?” ( jokinggg-no hyper-masculinity).

It sounds very much, based on this caption, that Rose and Edwards have already found out the gender of this impending little one.

Rose, meanwhile, is also the mother to a six-year old son she had with Wiz Khalifa.

She famously dated Kanye West several years ago as well.

Amber and Alexander haven’t flaunted their romance very much, but Rose gushed and gushed and then gushed some more over her boyfriend back in late January.

First, she posted this intense picture of her new baby daddy…

… and then she added the following tribute in his honor:

He thinks he soooo cute! He really is tho and sweet, smart, talented, charismatic and overall just an amazing man.

In the past I’ve used the words “best friend” very loosely while speaking of my ex’s but I can honestly say I feel like this man really is my BEST FRIEND! We talk for hours, he makes me a better person, he listens to me and understands me.

He also came into my life at a time where I’ve had enough of the narcissistic, cheating and abuse I’ve endured over the years from my previous relationships…..

Me always apologizing for things I had no business apologizing for, being gaslighted, manipulated and mentally abused.

I felt so damaged when I met him and pushed him away in the beginning, he has talked me through everything while simultaneously loving me and working with me so I could overcome my fear of loving someone in the most healthiest way again.

So @ae4president Thank you for all of ur love and support baby. I love you so much.

Based on how far along Rose appears to be in her ultrasound image, it’s very possible that Rose had just found out she and Alexander were expecting their child when she posted this caption.

Not that it matters in the big picture.

All that matters here is that the couple is happy and their have a baby on the way.

CONGRATS!
